# CCNA LAB 03 — RSTP Convergence vs 802.1D STP

## Objective

Build a redundant Layer 2 topology and compare:

* Rapid Spanning Tree Protocol (RSTP)
  VS
* Legacy IEEE 802.1D Spanning Tree

Simulate a link failure and measure:

* Convergence speed
* Packet loss duration
* STP state transitions
* Traffic recovery behavior

This lab demonstrates why RSTP replaced legacy STP in enterprise networks.

