# STEP 1 — BASIC CONFIGURATION

## DSW1

```cisco id="bw2s4k"
enable
configure terminal

hostname DSW1
no ip domain-lookup

spanning-tree mode pvst

vlan 10
 name USERS

interface range g0/1 - 2
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport mode trunk

spanning-tree vlan 10 root primary

end
write memory
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ASW1

# Configure legacy 802.1D STP

```cisco id="s34cg7"
enable
configure terminal

hostname ASW1
no ip domain-lookup

spanning-tree mode pvst

vlan 10
 name USERS

interface range g0/1 - 2
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport mode trunk

interface f0/1
 switchport mode access
 switchport access vlan 10
 spanning-tree portfast

end
write memory
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ASW2

# Configure RSTP

```cisco id="mfg27u"
enable
configure terminal

hostname ASW2
no ip domain-lookup

spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst

vlan 10
 name USERS

interface range g0/1 - 2
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport mode trunk

interface f0/1
 switchport mode access
 switchport access vlan 10
 spanning-tree portfast

end
write memory
```

