 shutdown

end
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# OBSERVE CONVERGENCE

Watch continuous ping.

Expected with legacy STP side involved:

* Multiple ping drops
* 30+ second outage possible

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# VERIFY STP TRANSITION

Run:

```cisco id="y8o8ti"
show spanning-tree vlan 10
```

Observe:

* Previously blocked port transitions:

  * Blocking
  * Listening
  * Learning
  * Forwarding

Classic 802.1D behavior.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

